{"tid":1569792,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［護警藍絲助攻］淘大義士被POPO扯爛衫時你地食花生？","createTime":"2019-09-14T17:54:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T08:53:39.000Z","uid":307047,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d4ebf9d82fd09217189b82fb3d37b89a1ff6b821","tid":1569792,"uid":307047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T17:54:45.000Z","msg":"14/9 今日下午3:31分<br />\n小妹以真街坊身分保衛淘大呢個家園<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一手拍下呢條片<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://gofile.io/?c=h5wwBK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgofile.io%2F%3Fc%3Dh5wwBK&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wb9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=78979451\" target=\"_blank\">https://gofile.io/?c=h5wwBK</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">屌曬你地班花生友</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1) 當時淘大四處戰線，眼前只有兩名黑警，但仍能以武力扯爛曬男義士的衣服，場面不堪入目<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你地班花生友有無諗過如果被扯衫嗰個係女仔咁會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢世仲洗見人嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">絕對唔可以再畀呢啲扯爛衫嘅情況發生</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2) 單以兩名黑警的能力，本來不足以控制當時混亂情況。但正正因為有兩名護警藍絲助攻<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />箍到義士條頸實一實走唔到，再加上左膠累事阻止阿嬸發攻拉走黑警，義士就咁被<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">黑警、藍絲、左膠聯成一線</span></strong></span>向義士施暴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n**值得留意：<br />\n<br />\n&mdash; 東九龍一直係建制派鐵票倉，藍絲多到嚇撚死你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 義士有難你地唔幫手即係藍絲、黑警嘅<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">幫兇</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&mdash; 我地唔需要捉鬼，但身處戰區一定要留意身邊人係咪護警藍絲，聽其言觀其行，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">保護手足係第一關鍵</span></span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3）義士被捉被打時，旁邊手足請<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">盡力拯救</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />救得一個得一個，只要見到落單黑警就盡一切力<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">打尻佢地</span></strong>，唔好再食花生啦屌曬你地啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n（小妹當時只是單獨一人本身又極細粒，身旁無記者，除咗屌左膠同拍片保護義士外，膽小如鼠嘅我只能眼白白睇住義士被施暴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我對你唔住啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n但⋯我有高清原片在手！已睇曬主流媒體的live video 正正無呢一幕，除咗影POPO大頭的兩位中年手足外，當時應該只有我影到較大、更多的picture。知道你已被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果你本人或義務律師需要我提供片段，請你聯絡我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下是片段中扯爛你衫的POPO number:<br />\n#2990<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GiPq45h.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGiPq45h.png&h=8056faaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n#15398<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pw0t2R9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPw0t2R9.png&h=385d6951&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">支持私了藍絲廢佬廢嬸</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家要盡力衝破呢個心理關口，淘大手足實在太斯文喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"1bcf40581e7050ff482fc9e4edf6faac82a69455","tid":1569792,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T17:57:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R4oZup8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR4oZup8.jpg&h=22278f49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/revenuetower87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frevenuetower87&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wb9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=2f84754c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/revenuetower87</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/tax87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftax87&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wb9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=1a3b5d83\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/tax87</a>"},{"pid":"8fc070c7ec7cbd399e2332e1514c4d33b1d50df9","tid":1569792,"uid":288351,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T18:00:28.000Z","msg":"介5介意組個街坊隊？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkmarrock\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkmarrock&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wb9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=38e93db6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkmarrock</a>"},{"pid":"79900a953dacbc7ccc8dfcf73afdcd4c1e8611ae","tid":1569792,"uid":321081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T18:10:57.000Z","msg":"而家好多藍絲拉人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />見到好多人跑既時候有個藍絲求其攬住個手足就係咁叫班狗過黎拉佢，點知藍絲都比狗打左兩棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好彩手足最後走甩咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffadb59f8828b62d06ac6b28d49b168f88f6bea8","tid":1569792,"uid":307047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T18:28:55.000Z","msg":"原來你地真係當義士係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">condom</span></span><br />\n無人推仲要負皮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01413731821fc7a8e9e633082cdf4e350369b5a2","tid":1569792,"uid":307047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8fc070c7ec7cbd399e2332e1514c4d33b1d50df9","tid":1569792,"uid":288351,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T18:00:28.000Z","msg":"介5介意組個街坊隊？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkmarrock\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkmarrock&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wb9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=38e93db6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkmarrock</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T18:30:45.000Z","msg":"小妹做緊文宣組喇分身不暇<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你有無入九龍灣之友TG呀？"},{"pid":"0b63db8c3ffc9c094cabb8cbe180301007882fa2","tid":1569792,"uid":307047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T02:14:31.000Z","msg":"我知我係P <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係咪無人理義士喇"},{"pid":"773daca5741e2df5d2c05f8ee683e62602c26c65","tid":1569792,"uid":307047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T02:15:27.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">救義士<span style=\"color: violet;\"></span></span>"},{"pid":"8e371e0b2ddc405b5bfabb0fc384f2a83a9da09b","tid":1569792,"uid":307047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T02:17:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">淘大義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"260f3d44873c10caeecf3dda0905e2fd6972edd2","tid":1569792,"uid":307047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T02:18:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: maroon;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>保護手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.g